OOC: If there is someone in the brig, I'll need to know who. 

::KitKat2::

She made her way around the brig of the allience base.  She thought 
she heard yelling coming from one of the cells, but she wasn't sure. 
It may be from elsewhere, she thought. 
Curiousity was getting the better of her and she started to look at 
the hostage list of the brig on the clip board near the guard 
station. "Hmmmmm."
